column5: Leaving tomorrow and we always go a certain way but our gps is telling us to a take a different way. Does anyone have any experience with this drive? Thanks, fish24/7
90/94 to Eau Claire, 53 to Intl falls. 11 over past Emo 71 To Kenora!
Construction in Duluth/Superior. Worse going south, bypass if you can.
Is the bypass open around Eau Claire
